features.name: AvrPtoB-E3_ubiq,AvrPtoB_bdg Effector protein that plays different roles depending on the species and plant cultivars that interact with the pathogen. Acts as a virulence determinant by enhancing the development of disease symptoms and bacterial growth. Acts as an avirulence factor by eliciting hypersensitive response (HR) and plant resistance (By similarity)
